[CONNECTION ESTABLISHED]

“Hello?! Are you here to help us??”

“Yes, I'll fix your electricity.”

“THANK GOD, FINALLY WE ARE SAVED! Our sheep have all died, and most of us are on the verge of starvation! Without power, our long range communications systems don't work… Now we can finally call for for help and food!”

“I'm sorry, I don't have any food with me right now. All I can do is redirect the laser.”

“That's enough, if you can do that! But please hurry!”

“I'll do my best!”
